  <h1>Google Review Response Examples for Every Business (2026)</h1>
  <div class="meta">Published April 2026 &bull; 10 min read &bull; By ReviewReply Team</div>

  <p>Responding to Google reviews is one of the most powerful — and most overlooked — local SEO strategies available. Yet most businesses either ignore reviews entirely or copy-paste the same generic response every time.</p>

  <p>Both approaches hurt your ranking and your reputation. This guide gives you <strong>ready-to-use response examples</strong> for restaurants, hotels, dentists, salons, and more — covering positive, negative, and neutral reviews.</p>

  <div class="highlight"><p>Tip: Always personalise these templates. Replace [Name], [specific detail], and [contact] with real information before sending.</p></div>

  <h2>Restaurant Review Response Examples</h2>

  <div class="industry-section">
    <div class="industry-title">&#127829; Restaurants</div>

    <h3>Positive review response</h3>
    <div class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
    <div class="review-text">"Best pizza in the city. The dough was perfect and the staff were so friendly. Will definitely come back!"</div>
    <div class="example">
      <div class="example-label">Your reply</div>
      <p>Thank you so much, [Name]! We are thrilled you enjoyed our pizza — our chef will love hearing this. Our team works hard to make every visit special and your kind words mean everything to us. We cannot wait to welcome you back to our restaurant soon!</p>
    </div>

    <h3>Negative review response</h3>
    <div class="stars" style="color:#EA4335">&#9733;&#9733;&#9734;&#9734;&#9734;</div>
    <div class="review-text">"Waited 45 minutes for our food on a Tuesday lunchtime. Not acceptable."</div>
    <div class="example">
      <div class="example-label">Your reply</div>
      <p>Thank you for your feedback, [Name]. We sincerely apologise for the long wait you experienced — 45 minutes for lunch is not the standard we hold ourselves to. We have reviewed our kitchen workflow for midweek service as a result. Please email us at [email] and we would love to offer you a complimentary meal on your next visit.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Hotel Review Response Examples</h2>

  <div class="industry-section">
    <div class="industry-title">&#127968; Hotels</div>

    <h3>Positive review response</h3>
    <div class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
    <div class="review-text">"Stunning views, spotless rooms and breakfast was incredible. Perfect stay."</div>
    <div class="example">
      <div class="example-label">Your reply</div>
      <p>What a wonderful review, [Name] — thank you! We are so pleased the views and breakfast made your stay memorable. Our housekeeping and kitchen teams take real pride in the experience we offer, and your feedback will be shared with the whole team. We hope to welcome you back to our hotel very soon!</p>
    </div>

    <h3>Negative review response</h3>
    <div class="stars" style="color:#EA4335">&#9733;&#9733;&#9734;&#9734;&#9734;</div>
    <div class="review-text">"Room was not properly cleaned when we arrived. Very disappointing for the price."</div>
    <div class="example">
      <div class="example-label">Your reply</div>
      <p>We are truly sorry to hear this, [Name]. A fully cleaned room on arrival is a basic standard we are committed to, and we clearly fell short during your stay. This has been addressed directly with our housekeeping team. Please contact our manager at [phone] — we would like to make this right for you.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Dental Clinic Review Response Examples</h2>

  <div class="industry-section">
    <div class="industry-title">&#129463; Dental Clinics</div>

    <h3>Positive review response</h3>
    <div class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
    <div class="review-text">"I was terrified of dentists but the team here made me feel completely at ease. Excellent care."</div>
    <div class="example">
      <div class="example-label">Your reply</div>
      <p>Thank you so much, [Name]! Helping nervous patients feel comfortable is something our dental team genuinely cares about, and your words truly mean a lot to us. We look forward to continuing to support your dental health. Do not hesitate to reach out if you ever have any questions between visits!</p>
    </div>

    <h3>Negative review response</h3>
    <div class="stars" style="color:#FBBC05">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9734;&#9734;</div>
    <div class="review-text">"Had to wait over 30 minutes past my appointment time. No apology from staff."</div>
    <div class="example">
      <div class="example-label">Your reply</div>
      <p>We sincerely apologise, [Name]. Keeping patients waiting without explanation or acknowledgement is not the standard of care we strive for. We have spoken with our reception team about communication during delays. Please call us at [phone] — we would like to personally apologise and ensure your next appointment runs smoothly.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Hair Salon Review Response Examples</h2>

  <div class="industry-section">
    <div class="industry-title">&#9986; Hair Salons</div>

    <h3>Positive review response</h3>
    <div class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
    <div class="review-text">"Best haircut I have had in years. The stylist really listened to what I wanted."</div>
    <div class="example">
      <div class="example-label">Your reply</div>
      <p>Thank you, [Name]! Our stylists love hearing this — truly listening to each client is at the heart of what we do at our salon. We will pass your compliment on to your stylist directly. We look forward to seeing you again for your next appointment!</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Tips for Writing Great Review Responses</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Use the reviewer's name</strong> when possible — it personalises the response instantly</li>
    <li><strong>Include a local keyword naturally</strong> — for example "our restaurant in [city]" helps local SEO</li>
    <li><strong>Keep it under 150 words</strong> — concise and genuine beats long and corporate</li>
    <li><strong>Never use the same response twice</strong> — Google notices and it looks robotic</li>
    <li><strong>Always respond within 24 hours</strong> — speed signals that you care</li>
  </ul>

